## Integration Points

### With GitHub
- Issue templates auto-populate when creating new issues
- Pre-configured with labels, checklists, acceptance criteria

### With CI/CD
```yaml
# Example: Validate critical tasks
- run: |
    INCOMPLETE=$(jq '.sections[] | select(.priority == "critical" and .status != "completed") | .id' docs/production_checklist.v1.json)
    [ -z "$INCOMPLETE" ] || exit 1
```

### With Cursor Agents
```typescript
const checklist = require('./docs/production_checklist.v1.json');
// Agent can read, filter, and update tasks
```

### With Scripts
```bash
# Check status
bash scripts/checklist-status.sh

# Query JSON
jq '.summary' docs/production_checklist.v1.json

# Find tasks
jq '.sections[] | select(.status != "completed")' docs/production_checklist.v1.json
```

